  "raw_answer": "∵S△ABC＝0.5×BC•hBC＝0.5×AC•hAC＝18，∴S△ABC＝0.5×（BD+CD）•hBC＝0.5×（AE+CE）•hAC＝18，∵AE＝CE＝0.5×AC，S△AEB＝0.5×AE•hAC，S△BCE＝0.5×EC•hAC，∴S△AEB＝S△CEB＝0.5×S△ABC＝0.5×18＝9，即S△AEF+S△ABF＝9①，同理：∵BD＝2CD，BD+CD＝BC，∴BD＝\\frac{2}{3}×BC，S△ABD＝0.5×BD•hBC，∴S△ABD＝\\frac{2}{3}×S△ABC＝\\frac{2}{3}×18＝12，即S△BDF+S△ABF＝12②，由①﹣②得：S△BDF﹣SAEF＝（S△BDF+S△ABF）﹣（S△AEF+S△ABF）＝12﹣9＝3．故选：A．"
